title: [Apple Orchard, Skull Hollow]
description: In the center of this section of the orchard stands a blackened hollow tree, a splintering sign nailed to what is left of its trunk.  The tangled, charred branches of the trunk reach out like skeletal arms, with only the filtered moonlight providing any deliverance from the illusion.

In the center of this section of the orchard stands a blackened hollow tree, a splintering sign nailed to what is left of its trunk.  The tangled, charred branches of the tree cast shadows in strange, chaotic patterns all about the hollow, causing the light to play tricks on the eyes.
